## Proposed Changes

### Komponen 1: Backend — Notification Deduplication

#### [MODIFY] [notification.service.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/backend/src/modules/notifications/notification.service.ts)

Tambah **deduplication check** di method `create()`:

```typescript
async create(data: { ... }): Promise<Notification> {
    // DEDUP: Check existing notification with same type + referenceId + userId within 24h
    if (data.referenceId) {
        const existing = await this.notificationRepo.findOne({
            where: {
                userId: data.userId,
                type: data.type,
                referenceId: data.referenceId,
                createdAt: MoreThan(new Date(Date.now() - 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000)),
            },
        });
        if (existing) {
            // Skip duplicate — return existing notification
            return existing;
        }
    }
    // ... rest of create logic
}
```

